ecause%20of%20a%20sympathy%20wave%20in%20favour%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20a%20senior%20leader%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%20has%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Mr%20Bhujbal%20also%20opened%20up%20on%20his%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20from%20contention%20for%20the%20Nashik%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20and%20shared%20his%20thoughts%20on%20whether%20the%20NDA's%20slogan%20for%20winning%20400%20seats%20-%20'%3Cem%3Eab%20ki%20baar%20400%20paar%3C%2Fem%3E'%20-%20has%20made%20voters%20believe%20that%20the%20Constitution%20will%20be%20amended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra's%20already%20interesting%20politics%20became%20more%20complex%20in%202022%20when%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20a%20group%20of%20MLAs%20staged%20a%20rebellion%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20government%20collapsing.%20Mr%20Shinde%20went%20on%20to%20align%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20take%20oath%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20splitting%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20into%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20a%20similar%20script%20played%20out%20in%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%2C%20when%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%20split%20the%20party%20and%20also%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20becoming%20a%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20process.%20The%20Maharashtra%20political%20landscape%2C%20thus%2C%20now%20has%20two%20Shiv%20Senas%20and%20two%20NCPs%20-%20under%20very%20similar%20but%20different%20names%20-%20pitted%20against%20each%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Bhujbal%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20rebellion%20in%20the%20NCP%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20this%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20he%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20there%20is%20a%20sympathy%20wave%20-%20the%20way%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%20split%20and%20a%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20switched%20sides.%20This%20is%20showing%20in%20their%20rallies.%20It%20doesn't%20seem%20like%20they%20are%20failing%20the%20way%20they%20did%20in%202014%20and%202019.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20of%20those%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20fought%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20parties%20had%20won%20in%2023%20and%2018%20constituencies%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people's%20faith%20is%2C%20however%2C%20still%20in%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20they%20want%20him%20to%20form%20a%20strong%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20minister%20turned%20slightly%20emotional%20when%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20contest%20in%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20bastion%20of%20Baramati%20between%20his%20daughter%20Supriya%20Sule%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20wife%2C%20Sunetra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20for%20me%2C%20it%20is%20saddening%2C%20that%20people%20who%20have%20lived%20together%20in%20the%20same%20house%20for%20so%20many%20years...%20What%20is%20happening%20is%20something%20that%20many%20people%20are%20not%20liking.%20Whose%20fault%20it%20is%2C%20that%20is%20a%20different%20matter.%20But%20it%20would%20have%20been%20very%20good%20if%20this%20had%20not%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESlogan%20Hurting%20NDA%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20opposition's%20charge%2C%20also%20made%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20that%20the%20NDA%20is%20seeking%20400%20seats%20because%20it%20wants%20to%20amend%20the%20Constitution%20and%20whether%20the%20%26quot%3Bab%20ki%20baar%20400%20paar%26quot%3B%20slogan%20has%20hurt%20the%20NDA%20alliance%2C%20Mr%20Bhujbal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20opposition's%20campaign%20on%20this%20has%20been%20a%20strong%20one.%20People%20think%20the%20slogan%20is%20about%20changing%20the%20Constitution.%20And%20a%20BJP%20MP%20in%20Karnataka%20(Anantkumar%20Hegde)%20had%20also%20said%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPM%20Modi%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%20several%20times%20that%20the%20Constitution%20is%20strong%20and%20it%20can't%20be%20changed%20even%20by%20BR%20Ambedkar%20himself.%20But%20this%20message%20is%20being%20given%20to%20the%20people.%20The%20impact%20will%20be%20seen%20only%20when%20the%20ballot%20boxes%20are%20opened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWithdrawal%20From%20Contest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENashik%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20contentious%20constituencies%20as%20the%20BJP%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20try%20to%20work%20out%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20and%20Mr%20Bhujbal%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20race%20for%20the%20ticket%20on%20Friday.%20The%20candidate%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20announced%20and%20a%20tussle%20between%20the%20allies%20seems%20to%20be%20underway%2C%20with%20conflicting%20remarks%20being%20made%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Pankaja%20Munde%20and%20chief%20minister%20Shinde.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhujbal%20said%20he%20had%20not%20asked%20for%20the%20ticket%20but%20was%20told%20by%20other%20leaders%20in%20the%20NCP%20during%20Holi%20that%20he%20would%20contest%20from%20Nashik.%20This%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20conveyed%20to%20him%20after%20a%20late-night%20meeting%20between%20the%20allies%20in%20Delhi%20where%20seats%20were%20being%20discussed%20one%20by%20one%20instead%20of%20in%20blocks%20for%20each%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20Mr%20Shinde%20also%20wanted%20the%20seat%20for%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20that%20he%20agreed%20to%20contest%20because%20Nashik%20is%20his%20base%20and%20he%20and%20his%20son%20have%20been%20MLAs%20from%20there.%20His%20nephew%2C%20Sameer%20Bhujbal%2C%20was%20also%20an%20MP%20from%20the%20seat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20he%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20from%20the%20people%20because%20of%20the%20development%20work%20he%20had%20done%2C%20Mr%20Bhujbal%20said%20he%20was%20surprised%20because%20his%20name%20was%20not%20declared%20from%20the%20seat%20for%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Narayan%20Rane's%20name%20was%20also%20declared%20(for%20Ratnagiri-Sindhudurg)%20and%20mine%20wasn't%2C%20I%20figured%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20do%20it.%20That's%20when%20I%20said%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20fight%20from%20the%20seat.%20If%20I%20have%20to%20contest%2C%20I%20want%20to%20do%20so%20with%20respect.%20I%20know%20my%20status.%20I%20don't%20like%20asking%20for%20tickets.%20The%20only%20time%20I%20asked%20for%20a%20ticket%20was%20from%20(Shiv%20Sena%20founder)%20Bal%20Thackeray%20for%20the%20municipal%20corporation%20in%20Mumbai%20in%201970%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%20I%20have%20been%20involved%20even%20in%20ticket%20distribution.%20So%20I%20thought%20waiting%20for%20so%20long%20is%20not%20right%20for%20me.%20So%20I%20felt%20bad%2C%20and%20decided%20not%20to%20contest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714238940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fcs97ro28_chhagan-bhujbal-interview_625x300_27_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-sympathy-wave-for-uddhav-thackeray-sharad-pawar-chhagan-bhujbal-5538107%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20NDA%20in%20Maharashtra%20may%20not%20have%20it%20as%20easy%20as%20it%20did%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20when%20it%20won%2041%20of%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20because%20of%20a%20sympathy%20wave%20in%20favour%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20a%20senior%20leader%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-sympathy-wave-for-uddhav-thacker