0Reuters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbytedance-rather-close-down-tiktok-us-than-sell-report-2024%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hardik%20Brutally%20Reminds%20MI%20Stars%20About%20'Game%20Awareness'%20After%20DC%20Defeat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20captain%20Hardik%20Pandya%20said%20he%20wanted%20batters%20to%20take%20chances%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%20and%20claimed%20MI%20were%20backing%20themselves%20to%20chase%20down%20the%20score%20in%20the%20end%20against%20Delhi%20Capitals%20(DC)%20at%20Arun%20Jaitley%20Stadium%20on%20Saturday.%20Fraser-McGurk%20equalled%20his%20own%20record%20for%20the%20fastest%20fifty%20in%20IPL%202024%2C%20smashing%2087%20off%2027%20balls%20to%20lay%20the%20groundwork%20for%20a%20massive%20total.%20DC%20scored%20257%20in%2020%20overs%2C%20with%20cameos%20from%20Shai%20Hope%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20and%20Tristan%20Stubbs.%20MI%20seemed%20to%20be%20always%20behind%20the%20chase%2C%20and%20Tilak%20Varma's%20brave%20effort%20was%20insufficient%20as%20Delhi%20prevailed%20by%2010%20runs.%20MI%20suffered%20their%20sixth%20loss%20of%20the%20season%2C%20jeopardising%20their%20playoff%20ambitions%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20the%20match%2C%20Pandya%20stated%20that%20the%20game%20was%20becoming%20increasingly%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20game%20is%20becoming%20more%20and%20more%20closer.%20It%20(the%20difference)%20used%20to%20be%20a%20couple%20of%20overs%2C%20now%20it's%20becoming%20a%20couple%20of%20balls.%20Because%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20games%20and%20how%20the%20bowlers%20are%20under%20pressure%2C%20we%20backed%20ourselves%20to%20do%20it.%20If%20I%20had%20to%20pick%20something%20out%2C%20we%20could%20have%20taken%20a%20couple%20of%20more%20chances%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%2C%26quot%3B%20Pand