quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20Anurag%20Thakur%20followed%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20the%20PM%20and%20the%20UP%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20made%20a%20most%20outrageous%20speech%20that%20violates%20all%20standards%20of%20decency%20and%20truth%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20EC's%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%40INCIndia%20has%20written%20to%20the%20ECI%20to%20take%20note%20of%20the%20speech%20and%20issue%20Mr.%20Thakur%20a%20notice%20immediately.%20The%20ECI%20must%20realise%20that%20a%20lack%20of%20meaningful%20action%20emboldens%20these%20bad%20faith%20actions.%20And%20if%20they%20do%20not%20take%20action%20then%20we%20will%20name%20and%20shame%20these%20offenders%20who%20think%20they%20are%20above%20the%20law%2C%20both%20in%20the%20arena%20of%20the%20public%20as%20well%20as%20before%20the%20courts%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20'X'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister's%20attack%20follows%20fierce%20sparring%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20top%20Opposition%20leaders%20over%20claims%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20seize%20the%20wealth%20of%20Indians%20and%20distribute%20it%20among%20Muslims.%20At%20rallies%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Tonk%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Sagar%2C%20the%20PM%20alleged%20that%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh-led%20Congress%20government%20had%20said%20Muslims%20have%20the%20first%20right%20to%20the%20country's%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20have%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row%2C%20with%20one%20section%20criticising%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20using%20expressions%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Binfiltrators%26quot%3B%20for%20Muslims%2C%20and%20another%20section%20slamming%20Dr%20Singh%20over%20his%20alleged%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20five-minute%20video%20message%20posted%20on%20the%20BJP's%20X%20handle%20yesterday%2C%20BJP%20party%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20also%20repeated%20controversial%20sections%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Rajasthan%20speech%20-%20in%20which%20he%20referred%20to%20Muslims%20and%20said%20the%20Congress%20plans%20to%20%26quot%3Bredistribute%20wealth%20to%20infiltrators%26quot%3B%20-%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20says%20Muslims%20have%20first%20right%20on%20country's%20resources%2C%20whereas%20PM%20Modi%20says%20poor%20people%20must%20have%20the%20first%20right%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20does%20not%20want%20Muslims%20to%20be%20neglected%E2%80%A6%20but%20they%20should%20not%20take%20undue%20advantage%20at%20expense%20of%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadda%20declared%2C%20as%20he%20slammed%20the%20Congress%20for%20%26quot%3Bappeasement%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20claimed%20such%20practices%20were%20evident%20in%20its%20manifesto%20-%20which%20the%20PM%20called%20a%20%26quot%3BMuslim%20League%20imprint%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakur%20and%20Mr%20Nadda's%20remarks%20come%20just%20days%20after%20the%20Election%20Commission%20sent%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20party%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20the%20Congress%20against%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20alleging%20he%20made%20divisive%20remarks%20during%20his%20Rajasthan%20speech.%20The%20notice%20-%20in%20a%20significant%20first%20-%20said%20party%20bosses%20would%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20Model%20Code%20violations%20in%20campaign%20speeches%20and%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20panel%20sent%20a%20nearly%20identical%20notice%20to%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20after%20the%20BJP%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20claiming%20he%20had%20made%20%26quot%3Bobnoxious%20utterances%26quot%3B%20against%20Mr%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20two-page%20statement%20-%20which%20did%20not%20name%20either%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20or%20Mr%20Gandhi%20but%20included%20copies%20of%20the%20complaints%20-%20the%20poll%20body%20said%20%26quot%3B'star%20campaigners'%20are%20expected%20to%20contribute%20to%20a%20higher%20quality%20of%20discourse...%20which%20sometimes%20gets%20distorted%20in%20the%20heat%20of%20contests%20at%20local%20level%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714234980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fam49q95s_anurag-thakur-1200_625x300_27_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felections-2024-congress-manifesto-row-minister-anurag-thakur-repeats-property-to-muslims-charge-against-congress-at-rally-5536112%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20Saturday%20morning%20-%20a%20day%20after%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20voting%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20-%20and%20claimed%20that%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bforeign%20forces%26quot%3B%20involved%20in%20preparing%20the%20poll%20manifesto%20of%20the%20opposition%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felections-2024-congress-manifesto-row-minister-anurag-thakur-repeats-property-to-muslims-charge-against-congress-at-rally-5536112%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felections-2024-congress-manifesto-row-minister-anurag-thakur-repeats-property-to-muslims-charge-against-congress-at-rally-5536112%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felections-2024-congress-manifesto-row-minister-anurag-thakur-repeats-property-to-muslims-charge-against-congress-at-rally-5536112%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iranian%20Rapper%20Toomaj%20Salehi%20Sentenced%20to%20Death%20Over%20Music%20Criticizing%20Government%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714234948000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FGettyImages-1455495504.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235984382%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iranian%20rapper%20Too