%20Ms%20Gandhi%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Latur%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20people%20have%20decided%20to%20vote%20out%20this%20government%20that%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20inflation%20and%20unemployment%20and%20bring%20in%20a%20dispensation%20that%20serves%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20speaking%20about%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Congress'%20guarantees%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20was%20interrupted%20by%20someone%20in%20the%20audience%20who%20chanted%20an%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eab%20ki%20baar%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20slogan%20in%20her%20party's%20favour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeizing%20on%20the%20opportunity%20to%20take%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20BJP%20and%20PM%20Modi%2C%20who%20have%20crystallised%20their%20target%20of%20the%20NDA%20winning%20400%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20into%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eab%20ki%20baar%20400%20paar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(this%20time%2C%20over%20400%20seats)%20slogan%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAb%20ki%20baar%20aap%20ki%20sarkar%2C%20ab%20ki%20baar%20janata%20ki%20sarkar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20You%20have%20suffered%20enough.%20PM%20Modi%20and%20all%20his%20ministers%20have%20understood%20that%20the%20people's%20mood%20is%20changing%2C%20that%20their%20drama%20and%20theatrics%20will%20no%20longer%20work%20and%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20will%20work%20is%20the%20truth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVoters%20want%20the%20truth%20and%20want%20to%20go%20back%20to%20their%20old%20religious%20tradition%20where%20every%20leader%20bows%20before%20the%20people%20and%20realises%20that%20he%20or%20she%20has%20a%20huge%20responsibility%20to%20them%2C%20the%20biggest%20being%20that%20the%20truth%20should%20be%20told.%20A%20leader's%20duty%20is%20to%20serve%20people%20and%20this%20is%20a%20tradition%20you%20have%20inculcated%20in%20politicians.%20But%20you%20are%20now%20stepping%20back%20and%20are%20now%20giving%20leaders%20the%20impression%20that%20they%20can%20talk%20about%20religion%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20do%20any%20work%20for%20voters%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20example%20of%20a%20voter%20she%20met%20in%20UP's%20Firozabad%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20woman%20told%20her%20that%20she%20would%20vote%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%20and%20caste.%20This%20mindset%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said%2C%20works%20in%20favour%20of%20leaders%20and%20their%20children%2C%20but%20not%20for%20the%20voters%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20vote%20is%20for%20roads%20in%20your%20area%2C%20schools%20for%20your%20children%2C%20water%20in%20your%20homes%20and%20for%20employment.%20Don't%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20leader%20or%20a%20party%2C%20vote%20in%20your%20own%20favour%2C%20for%20your%20family%2C%20village%2C%20city%20and%20country.%20Leaders%20get%20arrogant%20when%20in%20power%20and%20that's%20what%20you%20are%20seeing%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Mangalsutra'%20Rebuttal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20also%20issued%20a%20sharp%20response%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20claim%20of%20an%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bwealth%20redistribution%26quot%3B%20promise%20in%20her%20party's%20manifesto%20and%20said%20he%20is%20spreading%20misinformation%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20real%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20using%20his%20office%20to%20talk%20about%20things%20like%20the%20Congress%20stealing%20your%20'mangalsutras'.%20This%20country%20has%20seen%20so%20many%20great%20Prime%20Ministers%20-%20not%20just%20from%20the%20Congress%20-%20like%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20Manmohan%20Singh.%20But%20PM%20Modi%20has%20reduced%20the%20stature%20of%20the%20office%20so%20much%20that%20instead%20of%20asking%20for%20votes%20using%20his%20achievements%2C%20he%20is%20talking%20about%20a%20political%20party%20stealing%20your%20ornaments%20using%20an%20X-Ray%20machine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20the%20Congress'%20guarantees%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20contributed%20to%20its%20victory%20in%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20last%20year%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20their%20successful%20implementation%20is%20proof%20that%20the%20promises%20in%20its%20manifesto%20carry%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoters%20in%2013%20constituencies%20in%20Maharashtra%20have%20cast%20their%20ballots%20in%20the%20first%20two%20phases%20and%20eleven%20more%20seats%20will%20go%20to%20the%20polls%20in%20the%20third%20phase%20on%20May%207.%20The%20BJP%20and%20its%20ally%2C%20the%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20had%20won%2041%20of%20the%2048%20seats%20in%202019%20but%20the%20contest%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20much%20closer%20one%20this%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20are%20battling%20it%20out%20against%20a%20coalition%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714231260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fuubn7ujo_priyanka-gandhi_625x300_27_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fat-maharashtra-rally-priyanka-gandhis-ab-ki-baar-mantra-with-a-twist-5537087%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Giving%20a%20twist%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20slogan%20of%20%26quot%3Bab%20ki%20baar%20400%20paar%26quot%3B%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20has%20said%20the%20people%20have%20seen%20through%20the%20%26quot%3Blies%20and%20theatrics%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20current%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fat-maharashtra-