ot%20make%20the%20mistake%20of%20voting%20for%20%26quot%3Burban%20Naxals%26quot%3B%20and%20asserted%20that%20the%20Congress%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20are%20%26quot%3Banti-tribals%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Gujarat's%20Bharuch%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20where%20the%20AAP%20has%20fielded%20a%20candidate%20as%20part%20of%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20urged%20the%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20BJP's%20sitting%20MP%20Mansukh%20Vasava.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20will%20never%20get%20a%20public%20representative%20like%20Manuskh%20Vasava.%20If%20you%20make%20a%20mistake%2C%20then%20some%20urban%20Naxal%20will%20take%20his%20place%20(as%20MP)%20and%20destroy%20this%20tribal%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMansukh%20Vasava%20is%20pitted%20against%20the%20AAP's%20sitting%20MLA%20Chaitar%20Vasava%20in%20Bharuch%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20south%20Gujarat%2C%20which%20has%20a%20sizeable%20presence%20of%20tribals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20have%20come%20together%20to%20loot%20people.%20I%20have%20no%20hesitation%20in%20saying%20the%20Congress%20is%20an%20anti-tribal%20party%20and%20AAP%20will%20exploit%20tribals%20after%20getting%20their%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20are%20spreading%20rumours%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20change%20the%20Constitution%20and%20scrap%20reservation%20after%20it%20wins%20400%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bexpert%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal-led%20party%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Esardar%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(chieftain)%20in%20spreading%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20two%20liars%20have%20come%20together%20(as%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc)%20in%20Bharuch%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20in%20power%20for%20the%20past%2010%20years%20with%20a%20clear%20majority%20and%20could%20have%20changed%20the%20Constitution%20if%20it%20had%20any%20intention%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20here%20to%20tell%20you%20Modi's%20guarantee%20is%20that%20he%20will%20neither%20touch%20reservations%20for%20Adivasis%2C%20Dalits%20or%20OBCs%20nor%20will%20he%20allow%20anyone%20to%20touch%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20are%20spreading%20lies%20that%20the%20proposed%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20will%20take%20away%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20tribals%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20further%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20seen%20the%20UCC%20bill%2C%20and%20it%20says%20UCC%20does%20not%20apply%20to%20the%20tribals.%20They%20(Congress%20and%20AAP)%20are%20spreading%20lies.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20tell%20thousands%20of%20tribals%20sitting%20here%20that%20Chaitar%20Vasava%20(AAP%20candidate)%20and%20company%20are%20spreading%20lies.%20Do%20not%20fall%20for%20their%20words%20because%20Modi%20is%20a%20friend%20of%20Adivasis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20stalwart%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20Eklavya%20schools%20(residential%20schools%20for%20tribals)%20have%20risen%20from%2090%20under%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20rule%20to%20740%20now%2C%20while%20a%20district%20mineral%20fund%20has%20been%20set%20up%20with%20a%20corpus%20of%20Rs%2075%2C000%20crore%20to%20take%20care%20of%20water%2C%20education%2C%20health%20and%20nutrition%20needs%20of%20tribals%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacking%20the%20Congress%20on%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20issue%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20invited%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(for%20the%20idol%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20on%20January%2022)%20but%20they%20were%20concerned%20about%20their%20vote%20bank.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20Bharuch%20support%20those%20who%20do%20not%20participate%20in%20Lord%20Ram's%20idol%20consecration%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714230360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ff6lu67fg_amit-shah_625x300_27_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-gujarat-amit-shahs-urban-naxal-jibe-at-congress-aap-5537318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Saturday%20said%20people%20must%20not%20make%20the%20mistake%20of%20voting%20for%20%26quot%3Burban%20Naxals%26quot%3B%20and%20asserted%20that%20the%20Congress%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20are%20%26quot%3Banti-tribals%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-gujarat-amit-shahs-urban-naxal-jibe-at-congress-aap-5537318%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-gujarat-amit-shahs-urban-naxal-jibe-at-congress-aap-5537318%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-gujarat-amit-shahs-urban-naxal-jibe-at-congress-aap-5537318%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Police%20detain%20100%20as%20pro-Palestinian%20camp%20cleared%20at%20US%20university%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714230314000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109652052%2Cimgsize-2065587.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpolice-detain-100-as-pro-palestinian-camp-cleared-at-us-university%2Farticleshow%2F109651989.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109651989.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpolice-detain-100-as-pro-palestinian-camp-cleared-at-us-university%2Farticleshow%2F109651989.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpolice-detain-100-as-pro-palestinian-camp-cleared-at-us-university%2Famp_articleshow%2F109651989.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpolice-detain-100-as-pro-palestinian-camp-cleared-at-us-university%2Famp_articleshow%2F109651989.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Facts%20On%20Ujjwal%20Nikam%2C%20BJP's%20Candidate%20Who%20Replaced%20Poonam%20Mahajan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20chosen%20lawyer%20Ujjwal%20Nikam%20as%20its%20candidate%20for%20the%20Mumbai%20North%20Central%20constituency%2C%20replacing%20Poonam%20Mahajan.%20Mr%20Nikam%20is%20renowned%20for%20his%20role%20as%20the%20prosecutor%20in%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Mumbai%20North%20Central%20constituency%20in%20Maharashtra%20consists%20of%20six%20assembly%20segments%20and%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20May%2020.%20Votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20some%20facts%20on%20Ujjwal%20Nikam%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E1.%20Ujjwal%20Nikam%20was%20born%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Jalgaon%20on%20March%2030%2C%201953%2C%20to%20lawyer%20Deorao%20Madhavrao%20Nikam%20and%20Vimaladevi%2C%20a%20well-known%20freedom%20fighter.%20Mr%20Nikam%20has%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20Science%20degree%20and%20got%20his%20law%20degree%20from%20SS%20Maniyar%20Law%20College%20in%20Jalgaon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E2.%20Ujjwal%20Nikam%20has%20been%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20a%20few%20famous%20court%20cases.%20In%201991%2C%20he%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20convicting%20Ravinder%20Singh%20for%20the%20Kalyan%20bomb%20blast.%20His%20career%20took%20a%20major%20turn%20in%201993%20when%20he%20became%20the%20public%20prosecutor%20for%20the%20Mumbai%20serial%20blasts%20case.%20He%20worked%20for%20over%2014%20years%20in%20the%20special%20court%20established%20under%20the%20Terrorist%20and%20Disruptive%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E3.%20Ujjwal%20Nikam%20was%20the%20public%20prosecutor%20in%20the%20trial%20of%20Ajmal%20Kasab%2C%20the%20lone%20terrorist%20caught%20after%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks.%20He%20argued%20successfully%20for%20Kasab's%20death%20penalty.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E4.%20Ujjwal%20Nikam's%20legal%20career%20also%20includes%20several%20high-profile%20assignments%20such%20as%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20Bollywood%20producer%20and%20T%20series%20founder%20Gulshan%20Kumar%20in%201997.%20In%202006%2C%20Mr%20Nikam%20was%20also%20prosecutor%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20Pramod%20Mahajan%C2%A0who%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20his%20brother%20Pravin%20in%20April%202006%20following%20a%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E5.%20Mr%20Nikam%20was%20provided%20Z-plus%20security%20after%202009%2C%20when%20he%20became%20a%20prosecutor%20in%20the%2026%2F11%20case.%20In%202016%2C%20he%20was%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Shri%2C%20India's%20fourth-highest%20civilian%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714230180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fu227okh8_ujjwal-nikam-ani_625x300_27_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-ujjwal-nikam-bjp-candidate-from-mumbai-north-central-seat-5537096%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ujjwal%20Nikam%20is%20known%20for%20his%20role%20as%20the%20prosecutor%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20attacks%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-ujjwal-nikam-bjp-candidate-from-mumbai-north-central-seat-5537096%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-ujjwal-nikam-bjp-candidate-from-mumbai-north-central-seat-5537096%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-ujjwal-nikam-bjp-candidate-from-mumbai-north-central-seat-5537096%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ujjwal%20Nikam%2C%2026%2F11%20Prosecutor%2C%20Is%20BJP%20Pick%20For%20This%20Mumbai%20Constituency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20named%20lawyer%20Ujjwal%20Nikam%20who%20was%20the%20public%20prosecutor%20in%20the%20Mumbai%2026%2F11%20terror%20attacks%20as%20its%20candidate%20from%20Mumbai%20North%20Central%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%20Mr%20Nikam%20replaces%20Poonam%20Mahajan%2C%20the%20current%20MP%20from%20this%20seat%2C%20as%20the%20party's%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nikam%20was%20also%20the%20prosecutor%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20Pramod%20Mahajan%2C%20the%20father%20of%20Poonam%20Mahajan%2C%20who%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20his%20brother%20Pravin%20in%20April%202006%20following%20a%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20Mahajan%20was%20elected%20from%20the%20constituency%20in%202014%20and%202019.%20She%20is%20also%20a%20former%20president%20of%20the%20BJP's%20youth%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20leaders%20have%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20drop%20her%20was%20based%20on%20organisational%20feedback%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20years%2C%20you%20saw%20me%20fighting%20against%20the%20accused%20in%20court.%20But%20today%2C%20BJP%20has%20given%20me%20the%20responsibility%20for%20which%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20PM%20Modi%2C%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20Maharashtra%20BJP%20chief%20Chandrashekar%20Bawankule%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20Mumbai%20BJP%20chief%20Ashish%20Shelar%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nikam%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20politics%20is%20not%20for%20me%20but%20through%20you%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20tell%20everyone%20that%20the%20country's%20Constitution%2C%20laws%20and%20security%20would%20be%20my%20priorities...%20The%20constituency%20from%20where%20I%20have%20been%20told%20to%20contest%20is%20a%20very%20important%20constituency%20of%20Mumbai.%20This%20has%20been%20represented%20by%20late%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20Ramdas%20Athawale%2C%20and%20Poonam%20Mahajan.%20These%20people%20have%20always%20raised%20questions%20in%20parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20indications%20had%20been%20there%20for%20some%20time%20Poonam%20that%20Mahajan%20would%20be%20dropped%2C%20it%20was%20the%20party's%20search%20for%20her%20replacement%20that%20took%20time%2C%20sources%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20court%2C%20Mr%20Nikam%20is%20known%20for%20arguments%20replete%20with%20histrionics%20and%20one-liners.%20He%20is%20hardly%20ever%20boring%2C%20and%20lightens%20the%20atmosphere%20by%20punctuating%20serious%20arguments%20with%20humour.%20It%20will%20have%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20he%20can%20win%20the%20argument%20in%20the%20people's%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20fielded%20its%20city%20unit%20chief%20and%20Dharavi%20MLA%20Varsha%20Gaikwad%20from%20Mumbai%20North%20Central.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20in%20Mumbai%20is%20scheduled%20on%20May%2020%20in%20the%20fifth%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20BJP%20also%20named%20eight%20more%20candidates%20for%20the%20Odisha%20assembly%20polls%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20alongside%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714230120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fahqb48bo_ujjwal-nikam_625x300_27_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news