0Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20court's%20opinion%20cannot%20be%20blinded%20by%20stereotypical%20perception%20of%20any%20gender%20or%20profession%20and%20%26quot%3Bgender-neutrality%26quot%3B%20must%20permeate%20through%20every%20judgment%2C%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20said%20while%20setting%20aside%20an%20order%20discharging%20the%20husband%20of%20a%20police%20official%20of%20charges%20of%20cruelty%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20said%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20sessions%20court%20was%20not%20based%20on%20the%20principles%20of%20criminal%20jurisprudence%20and%20fair%20trial%20but%20on%20an%20%26quot%3Bunjustified%20perception%20and%20bias%26quot%3B%20that%20a%20police%20officer%20can%20never%20be%20a%20victim%20of%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20harbour%20assumptions%2C%20especially%20as%20a%20judge%2C%20that%20a%20woman%2C%20by%20virtue%20of%20her%20profession%20as%20a%20police%20officer%2C%20cannot%20possibly%20be%20a%20victim%20in%20her%20own%20personal%20or%20matrimonial%20life%2C%20is%20a%20form%20of%20injustice%20of%20its%20own%20kind%20and%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20kinds%20of%20perversity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20for%20the%20judges%20to%20not%20forget%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20being%20gender%20neutral%20while%20authoring%20judgments%20not%20only%20means%20that%20the%20terminology%20employed%20and%20words%20used%20in%20the%20judgment%20are%20to%20be%20gender%20neutral%20but%20also%20means%20that%20the%20mind%20of%20a%20judge%20ought%20to%20be%20free%20from%20preconceived%20notions%20or%20prejudices%20based%20on%20gender%20or%20profession.%20The%20essence%20of%20gender-neutrality%20must%20permeate%20through%20every%20line%20of%20a%20judgment%20and%20a%20judge%20must%20cultivate%20thoughts%20that%20are%20inherently%20gender-neutral%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%2C%20in%20its%20order%2C%20also%20called%20for%20integrating%20gender%20sensitivity%20in%20judicial%20education%20and%20asked%20the%20Delhi%20Judicial%20Academy%20to%20make%20it%20part%20of%20the%20curriculum%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20principles%20of%20justice%20and%20equality%20under%20the%20law%20were%20overlooked%2C%20and%20undue%20emphasis%20was%20laid%20on%20the%20gender%20and%20the%20professional%20background%20of%20the%20complainant%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20in%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20both%20the%20husband%20and%20the%20wife%20were%20working%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20but%20the%20position%20of%20the%20wife%20was%20held%20against%20her%20by%20the%20sessions%20court%20while%2C%20conversely%2C%20the%20accused%20husband%20was%20said%20to%20have%20not%20intimidated%20his%20wife%20on%20account%20of%20his%20professional%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20prime%20duty%20of%20judicial%20academies%20should%20be%20to%20ensure%20that%20judges%20do%20not%20see%20litigants%20through%20%26quot%3Bprisms%20of%20gender%20biasness%26quot%3B%20but%20write%20their%20judgments%20wearing%20%26quot%3Bspectacles%20of%20gender%20neutrality%2C%20impartiality%2C%20equality%26quot%3B%20while%20being%20aware%20of%20any%20hidden%20biases%20or%20perceptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20court%2C%20therefore%2C%20requests%20the%20Delhi%20Judicial%20Academy%20that%2C%20in%20view%20of%20today's%20rapidly%20changing%20world%2C%20issues%20such%20as%20gender%20equality%2C%20cultural%20diversity%2C%20etc%2C%20which%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20legal%20discourse%2C%20be%20made%20part%20of%20the%20curriculum%20and%20continuous%20judicial%20education%20programme%20conducted%20by%20the%20academy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20training%20will%20also%20foster%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20different%20perspectives%20and%20experiences%20and%20will%20help%20judges%20make%20more%20informed%20and%20equitable%20decisions%2C%20thereby%20enhancing%20public%20trust%20and%20confidence%20in%20the%20legal%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20further%20observed%20that%20professional%20life%20should%20go%20to%20a%20person's%20credit%2C%20and%20not%20discredit%2C%20and%20that%20despite%20wielding%20influence%20and%20leadership%20in%20their%20workplaces%2C%20women%20often%20find%20themselves%20powerless%20in%20their%20matrimonial%20homes%20and%20may%20get%20subjected%20to%20abuse%20and%20mistreatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20empowerment%20and%20success%20should%20at%20no%20cost%20be%20employed%20to%20their%20disadvantage%20to%20either%20diminish%20their%20status%20or%20deprive%20them%20of%20legal%20protection%20or%20privileges%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20woman%2C%20regardless%20of%20her%20position%20or%20background%2C%20deserves%20equal%20respect%2C%20recognition%2C%20and%20access%20to%20legal%20protections.%20This%20idea%20extends%20to%20men%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714226820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Fci455r18_delhi-high-court-650_625x300_28_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgender-neutrality-must-permeate-through-every-judgment-delhi-high-court-5535305%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20court's%20opinion%20cannot%20be%20blinded%20by%20stereotypical%20perception%20of%20any%20gender%20or%20profession%20and%20%26quot%3Bgender-neutrality%26quot%3B%20must%20permeate%20through%20every%20judgment%2C%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgender-