facing%20corruption%20charges%20join%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bput%20on%20the%20lap%26quot%3B%20and%20sent%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20or%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20latter's%20%26quot%3Bwords%20have%20lost%20credibility%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20also%20accusing%20him%20of%20trying%20to%20polarise%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20a%20few%20more%20days...%20when%20the%20names%20of%20candidates%20come%20from%20people%20to%20me%20and%20I%20sign%20the%20notification%2C%20it%20will%20be%20announced%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20candidates%20for%20Amethi%20and%20Rae%20Bareli%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20questioning%20Congress%20leaders%20for%20changing%20constituencies%20must%20also%20tell%20me%20how%20many%20times%20have%20(Atal%20Bihari)%20Vajpayee%20and%20(Lal%20Krishna)%20Advani%20changed%20their%20seats%2C%26quot%3B%20Kharge%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20BJP%20criticising%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20fighting%20the%20elections%20from%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20instead%20of%20Amethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20demand%20from%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%20and%20he%20went%20there.%20Leaders%20have%20to%20go%20as%20demanded%20by%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Gandhi%20contesting%20from%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Kharge%20alleged%2C%20%26quot%3BModi%20is%20trying%20to%20intimidate%20everyone%2C%20with%20either%20CBI%20or%20ED%20or%20something%20else.%26quot%3B%20Comparing%20PM%20Modi%20with%20his%20predecessor%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20his%2010%20years%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20did%20you%20ever%20hear%20Manmohan%20Singh%20talking%20about%20snatching%20someone's%20mangalsutra%3F%20Did%20he%20badmouth%20anyone%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSingh%20would%20make%20one%20statement%20and%20it%20would%20be%20printed%20worldwide.%20If%20Modi%20speaks%20and%20his%20words%20have%20no%20credibility%2C%20what%20can%20we%20do%20about%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20PM%20Modi's%20allegation%20that%20Congress'%20manifesto%20is%20about%20appeasement%20of%20Muslims%2C%20Kharge%20asserted%20that%20it%20is%20a%20document%20with%20assurances%20for%20everyone%2C%20from%20youths%20to%20farmers%2C%20workers%2C%20women%20and%20backward%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELashing%20out%20at%20the%20PM%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20should%20think%20before%20you%20speak.%20Our%20Nyays%20and%20guarantees%20are%20for%20everyone...%20when%20you%20are%20repeatedly%20saying%20it's%20for%20Muslims%2C%20you%20are%20polarising%2C%20dividing%20the%20people%20and%20one%20day%20you%20will%20repent.%26quot%3B%20Asked%20for%20his%20reaction%20to%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma's%20remark%20that%20%26quot%3BKharge%20should%20join%20the%20BJP%26quot%3B%2C%20following%20the%20Congress%20chief's%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3BModi%20should%20read%20the%20grand%20old%20party's%20manifesto%20first%2C%20then%20we%20can%20have%20a%20discussion%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20said%20he%20will%20speak%20to%20the%20PM%2C%20who%20is%20his%20opponent%20in%20Parliament%2C%20and%20not%20to%20a%20CM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20spoken%20to%20Modi%20and%20not%20your%20(Assam)%20CM%20because%20I%20am%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20I%20was%20also%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20I%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20competency%20in%20Parliamentary%20office%20as%20well...%20I%20will%20speak%20to%20Modi.%20Why%20he%20(Himanta)%20bothers%20about%20it%3F%20Let%20him%20face%20the%20people%20here%20(in%20Assam)%20and%20then%20speak%20about%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Kharge%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlleging%20that%20the%20BJP%20%26quot%3Brolls%20out%20the%20red%20carpet%26quot%3B%20for%20opposition%20party%20leaders%20facing%20corruption%20charges%20when%20they%20enter%20the%20party%20fold%2C%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20(BJP%20leaders)%20say%20that%20corrupt%20leaders%20will%20be%20put%20in%20jail%2C%20but%20when%20those%20same%20people%20join%20the%20BJP%2C%20they%20make%20them%20sit%20on%20their%20lap.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20there%20are%20many%20such%20examples%20of%20corrupt%20leaders%20from%20other%20parties%20joining%20the%20BJP%20and%20being%20made%20ministers%2C%20MLAs%20or%20Members%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20questioned%20turncoat%20leaders%20%26quot%3Bwho%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20Congress%20and%20later%20left%20it%26quot%3B%20that%20if%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20was%20%26quot%3Bso%20bad%2C%20why%20did%20they%20waste%2030-40%20years%26quot%3B%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20is%20like%20a%20flowing%20river%2C%20it%20is%20not%20affected%20by%20a%20few%20persons%20leaving%20it.%20It%20is%20more%20than%20a%20century-old%20party.%20It%20has%20a%20history%20of%20making%20India%20independent%20and%20giving%20it%20democracy%20and%20a%20constitution.%20We%20have%20shown%20that%20democracy%20has%20sustained%20in%20India%20only%20due%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20president%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20the%20contribution%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20freed%20the%20country%20are%20in%20the%20Congress.%20No%20one%20from%20the%20BJP%20had%20fought%20for%20Independence%20or%20development.%20They%20talk%20about%20patriotism%20and%20try%20to%20project%20that%20(Jawaharlal)%20Nehru%2C%20Indira%20(Gandhi)%20and%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20were%20nothing%20in%20front%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20only%20Modi%20for%20them%20and%20they%20think%20India%20attained%20Independence%20in%202014%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20maintained%20that%20the%20ongoing%20elections%20are%20about%20%26quot%3Bsustaining%20democracy%20and%20saving%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20in%20the%20government%2C%20especially%20Modi%2C%20said%20they%20are%20for%20'%3Cem%3Esabka%20saath%2C%20sabka%20vikas%3C%2Fem%3E'.%20But%20actually%20what%20happened%20was%20%3Cem%3E'sabka%20satyanaash%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20Congress%20failed%20to%20make%20electoral%20bonds%20a%20poll%20issue%2C%20the%20party%20chief%20said%20it%20has%20raised%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20saying%20there%20is%20no%20level%20playing%20field.%20Loss-making%20companies%20were%20giving%20them%20(BJP)%20donations%20of%20Rs%20500-1%2C000%20crore.%20It%20was%20'%3Cem%3Echanda%20do%2C%20dhanda%20lo%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714226100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ffsnkaqn8_mallikarjun-kharge_625x300_27_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwait-for-few-more-days-congress-chief-mallikarjun-kharge-on-amethi-rae-bareli-picks-5536382%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20on%20Saturday%20said%20that%20the%20names%20of%20party%20candidates%20for%20the%20prestigious%20Amethi%20and%20Rae%20Bareli%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bfew%20days%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwait-for-few-more-days-congress-chief-mallikarjun-kharge-on-amethi-rae-bareli-picks-5536382%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-n