Cp%3EJyoti%20Cariappa%20Saikia%20(67)%2C%20a%20staunch%20devotee%20of%20Shri%20Aurobindo%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20also%20credited%20with%20inspiring%20the%20Auroville%20Township%20project%20%E2%80%94%20would%20make%20frequent%20trips%20to%20Puducherry.%20It%20would%20be%20lovely%20to%20have%20a%20place%20of%20my%20own%2C%20she%20thought.%20But%20months%20of%20scouting%20for%20apartments%20yielded%20no%20results.%20Until%20one%20day%2C%20in%202004%2C%20when%20Jyoti%20spotted%20a%20crumbling%20home%20that%20was%20up%20for%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20owner%2C%20an%20elderly%20woman%20in%20her%20seventies%20was%20looking%20to%20relocate%20to%20Marseille%20in%20France%20where%20her%20children%20had%20moved.%20Elated%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpure%20coincidence%E2%80%9D%2C%20Jyoti%20made%20an%20offer%20for%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20the%20reason%20for%20her%20spur-of-the-moment%20decision%2C%20she%20says%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344261%2Fbest-resorts-in-andaman-islands-barefoot-havelock-by-samit-sawhny-sustainable-slow-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20special%20vibe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20made%20it%20impossible%20to%20walk%20away%20even%20though%20I%20had%20set%20out%20looking%20for%20a%20smaller%20and%20easier-to-maintain%20apartment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reiterates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20blame%20her.%20The%20200-year-old%20tale%20of%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20would%20pale%20any%20history%20lesson%20in%20comparison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20watched%20the%20world%20evolve%3B%20from%20the%2018th%20century%20%E2%80%94%20when%20Puducherry%20was%20rife%20with%20traders%2C%20engineers%20and%20builders%20who%20came%20to%20work%20with%20the%20French%20East%20India%20Company%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20present%20day.%20It%20is%20undeniable%20that%20the%20French%20left%20their%20indelible%20imprint%20on%20the%20city%3B%20the%20town%20still%20reflects%20French%20sensibilities%20in%20the%20language%2C%20art%2C%20culture%20and%20the%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCSi6u7Cjlww%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCSi6u7Cjlww%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCSi6u7Cjlww%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Kitty%20%26amp%3B%20Navin%20(%40thenextcheckin)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20is%20one%20of%20history%E2%80%99s%20best-kept%20secrets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311053%2Fdushyant-vashisht-turned-cottage-to-sustainable-homestay-bir-terraces-uttarakhand-tourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estory%20of%20the%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20traces%20back%20to%20the%20early%201700s%20when%20Abraham%20Guerre%2C%20from%20the%20French-speaking%20province%20of%20St.Imier%20in%20Switzerland%2C%20came%20to%20Puducherry%20to%20work%20as%20a%20hospital%20administrator%20with%20the%20French%20East%20India%20Company.%20Abraham%20and%20his%20wife%20Marie%20Brunet%20had%20nine%20children%2C%20the%20third%20of%20whom%20Jacques%20Guerre%20inherited%20the%20house%20and%20sold%20it%20to%20a%20gentleman%20Francois%20Ulmans%20Marie%20Clark%20Michel%20in%201940.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20one%20of%20Francois%E2%80%99s%20descendants%20who%20sold%20the%20home%20to%20Jyoti%2C%20who%20saw%20the%20location%20as%20an%20incentive%20to%20be%20in%20close%20quarters%20to%20the%20Sri%20Aurobindo%20Ashram.%20Her%20mind%20was%20already%20racing%20with%20ideas%20of%20restoring%20the%20property%20to%20its%20original%20glory%2C%20equipping%20it%20with%20amenities%20while%20preserving%20its%20ancient%20mystique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG2_11zon-1713415777-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20rooms%20at%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20are%20furnished%20keeping%20the%20French%20style%20in%20mind%20and%20wood%20is%20sourced%20from%20demolished%20homes%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG2_11zon-1713415777-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG2_11zon-1713415777-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG2_11zon-1713415777-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG2_11zon-1713415777-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG2_11zon-1713415777-96x96.jpg%2096w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG2_11zon-1713415777.jpg%201440w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347589%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20rooms%20at%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20are%20furnished%20keeping%20the%20French%20style%20in%20mind%20and%20wood%20is%20sourced%20from%20demolished%20homes%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Siddarth%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Much%20of%20the%20old%20house%20has%20been%20preserved%20to%20give%20the%20home%20a%20touch%20of%20vintage%20magic%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861-768x960.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861-1229x1536.jpg%201229w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861-150x188.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861.jpg%201440w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347590%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMuch%20of%20the%20old%20house%20has%20been%20preserved%20to%20give%20the%20home%20a%20touch%20of%20vintage%20magic%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Siddarth%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyoti%20credits%20architect%20Ajit%20Koujalgi%20of%20INTACH%20(Indian%20National%20Trust%20for%20Art%20and%20Cultural%20Heritage)%20for%20lending%20his%20expertise%20to%20see%20this%20to%20fruition.%20She%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20some%20interesting%20side%20trips%20looking%20for%20authentic%20doors%2C%20windows%2C%20and%20wooden%20beams%20to%20restore%20and%20build%20the%20property.%20It%20was%20challenging%20and%20time-consuming%20but%20mostly%20enjoyable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20this%2C%20Siddarth%20says%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327062%2Fsanjay-austa-started-meena-bagh-homes-shimla-ratari-himachal-sustainable-homestay-stargazing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoal%20of%20the%20restoration%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20to%20be%20as%20historically%20accurate%20as%20possible.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20hundred%20percent%20authentic.%E2%80%9D%20With%20heritage%20becoming%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbuzzword%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20uncommon%20to%20hear%20of%20ancient%20buildings%20being%20razed%20in%20Puducherry%20to%20make%20way%20for%20brand-new%20residences.%20He%20did%20not%20want%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20to%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20keep%20the%20architectural%20motifs%20intact%20but%20restore%20the%20place%20using%20new%20materials%20and%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20pictures%20and%20decor%20that%20you%20see%20around%20the%20place%20are%20borrowed%20from%20one%20of%20Francois%E2%80%99%20ancestors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKeeping%20history%20intact%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20these%20pictures%20are%20giving%20you%20a%20deja%20vu%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20explain.%20The%20facade%20of%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20critically%20acclaimed%20film%20Life%20of%20Pi%20(2012).%20You%20might%20remember%20it%20from%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%2C%20Siddarth%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20director%20and%20the%20production%20team%20of%20the%20film%20wanted%20to%20shoot%20in%20Puducherry%20and%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20us.%20The%20facade%20features%20in%20one%20of%20the%20opening%20scenes.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20the%20photography%20team%20and%20cinematographer%20director%20stayed%20at%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20during%20the%20filming%20of%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20has%20seen%20its%20share%20of%20fame.%20In%202019%2C%20it%20featured%20in%20a%20BBC%20travel%20documentary%20series%20%E2%80%98The%20Real%20Marigold%20Hotel%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20accolades%20are%20merely%20feathers%20in%20its%20cap.%20The%20real%20success%20lies%20in%20its%20restoration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20736px)%20100vw%2C%20736px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22736%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gratitude%20Heritage%20is%20a%20200%20year%20old%20home%20that%20is%20built%20with%20a%20blend%20of%20French%20and%20Tamil%20architectural%20practices%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229.jpg%20736w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229-300x209.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229-500x349.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229-150x105.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347592%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22513%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGratitude%20Heritage%20is%20a%20200-year-old%20home%20that%20is%20built%20with%20a%20blend%20of%20French%20and%20Tamil%20architectural%20practices%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Siddarth%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%2050